{
  "title": "Creamy Savory Italian Bryndza Cheese Risotto",
  "description": "A rich and creamy Italian dish featuring bryndza cheese, perfect for a romantic dinner. This pressure-cooked risotto is a savory delight with a dash of Italian flair.",
